structure.unit: MORTGAGE LOAN COMPANIES AND LOAN BROKERS

law.history: Repealed 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 218, sec. 15, effective July 12, 2006. -- Created 2003 Ky. Acts ch. 64, sec. 8, effective June 24, 2003.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Denial, suspension, or revocation of license of mortgage loan company, mortgage loan broker, or loan officer.
